      <title>特朗普检察官面临最后期限，纽约封口费案悬而未决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/trump-da-faces-key-deadline-as-new-york-hush-money-case-in-limbo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赢得唐纳德·特朗普唯一一次刑事定罪的曼哈顿检察官面临周二的最后期限，他将陈述他认为鉴于前总统的连任该案应如何进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/trump-da-faces-key-deadline-as-new-york-hush-money-case-in-limbo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 20:34:32 GMT</pubDate>
